        public void testPassengersBoardsToPassengerCar()
                                        throws TrainException
        Create board() method in PassengerCar class which taken a parameter newPassengers in Integer data type. This method should return the number of passengers in Integer data type which do not able to board due to the limited number of seats and return 0 if all passenger can board. This test would supply newPassenger less than number of seats and expected return 0;
